Instructions:

    1. Select the cpu scheduling algorithm to simulate on the dropdown box.
    2. Input the Process ID, Arrival Time, Burst Time, Priority (if applicable to algorithm), and Time Quantum 
       (if applicable to algorithm) in the input fields.
    3. Click the ▶ Run button to run the simulation, the ⏸ Pause button to pause the simulation or ▶ Resume button
       to resume the simulation, and the ⏭ Step button to see the step by step simulation.

